      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but the thing is the basal is like my background insulin, not the one for food. since i barely ate anything to begin with, shouldn't the dose be way less necessary? i just don't want to wake up at 3am with a hypoglycemic episode because i took a full dose on an empty stomach. it feels safer to just skip it tonight than to risk a crash, right?",
